.********************************************************************** 00370000
.* Upon return:                                                         00380000
.* &BXA_RC     will contain 0 if a valid license was accepted           00390000
.*                          4 if license (version) is not valid         00400000
.*                          8 if license was not accepted               00410000
.*                         12 for internal errors                       00420000
.*                                                                      00430000
         GBLC  &SP_LICENSE             * License name / version         00440000
         GBLC  &SP_LICSTAT             * License status                 00450000
         GBLA  &BXA_RC                 * Return code                    00460000
&BXA_RC  SETA  12                      * Assume internal error          00470000
.*                                                                      00480000
.* Check whether the license was accepted                               00490000
         AIF   ('&SP_LICSTAT' EQ 'IAGREE').AGREED                       00500000
